methods.name: Call
methods.description: Calls the procedure in the current screen with the given name.

methods.name: CallAfterDelay
methods.description: Calls the procedure on the UI thread after waiting delay milliseconds on a separate thread.

methods.name: CallAfterDelayWithArgs
methods.description: Calls the procedure on the UI thread with the given arguments after waiting delay milliseconds on a separate thread.

methods.name: CallAsynchronous
methods.description: Calls the procedure in the current screen on a thread separate from the UI thread.

methods.name: CallAsynchronousWithArgs
methods.description: Calls the procedure in the current screen on a thread separate from the UI thread with the given list of arguments.

methods.name: CallWithArgs
methods.description: Calls the procedure in the current screen with a list of arguments.

name: AsyncProc
helpString: Extension Made From FuncCall. Edited by Abhijith. More extension at : https://simplegamers.co/appinv/store

events.name: CallFinishedWithResult
events.description: After an asynchronous procedure call, this event is run with the results of the invocation.
